        SP_AUGMENT["рҹӨ– Augment Code\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\nAI coding assistant\nUsed throughout development\nContext-aware completions\nSeamless refactoring"]
    end

